result.name: Fung Shing Restaurant

reviews.text: Foods and services are not that bad. We tried a special menu, steaming sea food on a tower. It looked gorgeous and tasted good. Particularly the congee cooked during the steaming was wonderful. But the actual amount was not enough for four, so that we had to order more dishes after that.
Great value dim sum and Chinese dinner!
Pretty safe as a DIMSUM place and eatery for Chinese cuisine. One of the many varieties of restaurants in this food court and neighborhood.
Reasonable price and fine service
reasonable price for old style Chinese dishes

reviews.text: 紅磡黃埔鳳城 碗筷不甚乾淨 杯底油淋淋 有飯黐住喺碗， 碗裏面有滑潺潺的感覺 似乎盛載過飯和粥 ，好像之前客人用後清洗不妥，枱布也污糟， 點心一般質素。

Foods and services are not that bad. We tried a special menu, steaming sea food on a tower. It looked gorgeous and tasted good. Particularly the congee cooked during the steaming was wonderful. But the actual amount was not enough for four, so that we had to order more dishes after that.
中式酒樓,蛋散ㄧ定要試。
地方大，易搵位，價錢中上。飯後有甜品送
